Babe and Dom.

300
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,839
This is for you, Teerak.

301
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,160
Thank you.

302
00:22:20,079 --> 00:22:21,160
Muenfah.

303
00:22:21,170 --> 00:22:22,220
[Muenfah]

304
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:28,849
- Thank you.
- Alright.

305
00:22:29,559 --> 00:22:33,119
You should get going now, or you'll be late.

306
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,730
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

307
00:22:34,769 --> 00:22:36,369
- Thank you so much.
- Drive safely, okay?

308
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:39,920
- Don't rush, alright?
- Yes.

309
00:22:40,319 --> 00:22:42,519
After you guys talked it out,

310
00:22:42,759 --> 00:22:45,359
can you feel that he's so much happier now?

311
00:22:45,559 --> 00:22:48,160
Thank you so much for figuring it out with him.

312
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:49,799
- That's so sweet of you.
- Okay.

313
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:14,240
Aren't you too calm now?

314
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:16,759
We're running late,
and we might not have time for breakfast.

315
00:23:18,119 --> 00:23:19,759
I knew it; I knew you'd be complaining.

316
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,440
I've prepared it for you.

317
00:23:29,759 --> 00:23:31,890
Here you go.

318
00:23:36,519 --> 00:23:37,839
When did you buy this?

319
00:23:38,359 --> 00:23:39,359
I made it myself.

320
00:23:43,359 --> 00:23:44,640
Told you.

321
00:23:45,519 --> 00:23:47,190
Whoever becomes my lover

322
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,630
is one lucky person.

323
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,619
Wanna become one?

324
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:59,799
What are you talking about? Hurry up.

325
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:03,559
Look at you.

326
00:24:07,119 --> 00:24:08,000
There you are.

327
00:24:12,119 --> 00:24:13,920
You gave it to me, didn't you?

328
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:16,000
Tell me your heart's fluttering.

329
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,640
Give it to me!

330
00:24:40,119 --> 00:24:41,200
Is your heart fluttering?

331
00:24:44,039 --> 00:24:45,519
Tell me it is.

332
00:25:01,359 --> 00:25:03,859
Told you we had 20 minutes.

333
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:05,150
That's more than enough.

334
00:25:05,559 --> 00:25:06,460
Whatever.

335
00:25:07,119 --> 00:25:08,529
Oh, Lee!

336
00:25:08,569 --> 00:25:10,440
- Oh...
- Hi, Real and Hia.

337
00:25:11,039 --> 00:25:12,160
Is Fah not here yet?

338
00:25:13,039 --> 00:25:13,920
What?

339
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:16,240
He's supposed to be with Teerak, isn't he?

340
00:25:16,279 --> 00:25:17,519
There they are.

341
00:25:18,839 --> 00:25:20,440
- Hey.
- Look at them.

342
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,359
Hello.

343
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:25,640
I'm happy that you're happy.

344
00:25:26,839 --> 00:25:28,039
I've talked it out with my dad.

345
00:25:28,079 --> 00:25:29,230
Seriously?

346
00:25:29,559 --> 00:25:31,440
Whoa, congrats.

347
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:34,039
This calls for a celebration!

348
00:25:34,839 --> 00:25:36,059
Let's have dinner at your bar.

349
00:25:36,099 --> 00:25:36,900
Hey,

350
00:25:37,079 --> 00:25:38,680
